---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Style Guide"
description: "Clean Arcade design system — colors, typography, and components."
permalink: /style-guide/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<div class="content-page">
  <p class="page-intro">Design tokens, components, and patterns used across Clean Arcade.</p>

  <div class="style-section">
    <h2>Colors</h2>
    <h3>Core palette</h3>
    <div class="color-swatches">
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--navy-950);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Navy 950</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#0f172a</div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--navy-900);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Navy 900</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#1e293b</div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--accent);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Accent</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#6366f1</div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--accent-hover);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Accent Hover</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#4f46e5</div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--green);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Green</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#22c55e</div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--red);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Red</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#ef4444</div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-swatch">
        <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--amber);"></div>
        <div class="color-swatch__label">Amber</div>
        <div class="color-swatch__value">#f59e0b</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Category colors</h3>
    <div class="color-swatches">
      {% for cat in categories %}
        <div class="color-swatch">
          <div class="color-swatch__preview" style="background: var(--cat-{{ cat.slug }});"></div>
          <div class="color-swatch__label">{{ cat.label }}</div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="style-section">
    <h2>Typography</h2>
    <div class="type-sample">
      <h1 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Heading 1 — Space Grotesk</h1>
      <h2 style="border: none; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Heading 2 — Space Grotesk</h2>
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Heading 3 — Space Grotesk</h3>
      <p>Body text — Inter. Clean Arcade is built on a simple idea: games should be fun, not frustrating.</p>
      <p class="text-muted">Muted text for secondary information and descriptions.</p>
    </div>
    <p>Display font: <strong>Space Grotesk</strong> (headings, version badges, nav labels)<br>
    Body font: <strong>Inter</strong> (everything else)<br>
    Served via <a href="https://fonts.bunny.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bunny Fonts</a> (GDPR-compliant).</p>
  </div>

  <div class="style-section">
    <h2>Buttons</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;">
      <button class="btn btn--primary">Primary</button>
      <button class="btn btn--outline">Outline</button>
      <button class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">Small</button>
      <button class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Large</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="style-section">
    <h2>Badges</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-sm); flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <span class="badge badge--category">Category</span>
      <span class="badge badge--easy">Easy</span>
      <span class="badge badge--medium">Medium</span>
      <span class="badge badge--hard">Hard</span>
      <span class="badge badge--mobile">Mobile OK</span>
      <span class="badge badge--desktop">Desktop only</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="style-section">
    <h2>Components</h2>

    <h3>Game filter bar</h3>
    <p>Category dropdown, A-Z letter filter, and search input. All filtering is client-side JavaScript.</p>

    <h3>Game cards</h3>
    <p>Auto-fill grid (min 160px mobile, 180px desktop). Each card shows game title on a colored placeholder background using the category color variable.</p>

    <h3>Game embed</h3>
    <p>Full-width on mobile, max 960px centered on desktop. Control bar with back, info, and share buttons. Info overlay for game controls and description.</p>

    <h3>Hamburger menu</h3>
    <p>Slide-in panel from right. Contains search, theme toggle, translate, main navigation, resources section (About, Blog, Changelog, Sitemap, Style Guide), legal links, and footer credit.</p>

    <h3>Dark mode</h3>
    <p>System preference detection with manual toggle. Inline script in <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> prevents flash. Theme stored in <code>localStorage["theme"]</code>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="style-section">
    <h2>Spacing scale</h2>
    <p>Based on a consistent scale from <code>--space-xs</code> (0.25rem) to <code>--space-3xl</code> (4rem). Section padding uses <code>clamp(3rem, 2rem + 4vw, 6rem)</code> for fluid scaling.</p>
  </div>
</div>
